      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that's been treated with care, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
