    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal mechanical grip. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis is sharpened with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the platform's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain is mechanically robust, offering the raw, naturally aspirated performance and linear power delivery defining this era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
